data.description: Welcome to this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom split foyer home with a large, finished bonus room in the basement. The primary bathroom boasts an oversized tub/shower combo and a convenient walk-in closet. The basement's huge bonus room features LVP floors and an acoustic drop ceiling, making it a versatile space for your needs. Enjoy privacy in the backyard, which features a charming pergola on the back deck and professional landscaping. There's also a storage building for your lawn equipment. The roof and upgraded 6" gutters are only 2.5 years old, ensuring peace of mind. The HVAC system is a reliable 4 years old, and the water heater is less than a year old, providing efficient living. Plus, a full home water filtration system installed less than a year ago ensures you have access to clean and pure water. MOTIVATED SELLERS are ready to make a deal as they have a new home in mind. Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to make this well-maintained and updated home your own!
